                                                                           int from,

                                                                           T n)
        The binarySearchIterative method searches a pre-sorted list for a given value using an iterative implementation of the binary search algorithm. If the value is not found, it returns -1. This is not a stable search (the original ordering of elements is not necessarily preserved). Running time:

        • worst O(log n)
        • best O(1)
        Memory Usage:
        • O(1)
